{
  "chapter": 17,
  "chapter_summary": "第十七回\"燃烧\"中，朱五太爷向小马介绍完颜兄弟——两名身材魁梧的胡人武者，分别精通十三太保横练和金钟罩铁布杉，双拳重逾千斤。小马被要求与完颜兄弟比拳，他以游鱼般的身法躲过两人的合击，导致完颜兄弟自相残杀。小马随后逐一击败二人，却对他们的忠诚与骨气深感敬佩。朱五太爷冷酷地表示\"没有用的人留着何益\"，小马愤怒质问其为何不阻止。朱五太爷承认小马的拳头是杀人利器，却质疑其忠心，以水能载舟覆舟为喻拖延决定。小马急于离开时，朱五太爷透露常无意也已来到此处。常无意现身，面容苍老十岁，与小马短暂寒暄后面对朱五太爷。朱五太爷试探常无意的杀人能力，常无意冷酷回应\"不但杀人，而且剥皮\"，声称自己有剑在手。朱五太爷最终同样让他坐下。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你左边的一个人叫完颜铁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他是童子功，十三太保横练。左拳击出，重五百斤，右拳重五百七十斤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "好，好拳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你右边的一个，叫完颜钢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他也是从小的童子功，金钟罩、铁布杉的功夫，刀枪难入。他的右手一拳重四百斤，左拳一击却至少有七百斤重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "好，好拳头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他们都是胡儿，单纯质朴，毫无机心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我看得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他们不但已将拳头奉献给我，连他们的命也献给了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我也看得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "有了他们，我为什么还要你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "因为我既不单纯，又有机心，所以我比他们有用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "可是现在他们这两拳头若是同时击下，你会怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你想不想试试他们的拳头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "很想。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你真的很想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "真的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你不后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "言既出，永无后悔。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wan_yan_tie",
      "text": "好汉子！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "你为什么一定要这样做？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "怎么样做？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "你本来早就可以阻止他们的，你早就应看得出他们没有机会。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "一个没有用的人，留着又有何益，毁了又有何妨？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "其实他们刚才本可毁了你的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "刚才的胜负之分，只不过在刹那之间，连我都想不到你敢用那样的险招。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "要死中求活，用招就不能不险。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你好大的胆。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我的胆子本来就不小。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "坐。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这一次我要你坐下，已不是为了你以前做的事，而是因为你的拳头。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只不过你有坐还是未必有命。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "你还不肯收下这双拳头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我已看出你这双拳头，的确是杀人的利器。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只不过杀人的利器，未必就是忠心的伙伴。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "水能载舟，也能覆舟。若将杀人利器留在身边，而不知它是否忠心听命，那岂非更危险？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "要怎么样你才相信我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我至少还得多考虑考虑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "你不能再考虑。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "你有时间考虑，我已没有，你若不肯助我，我只有走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你能走得了？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "至少我可以试试看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "至少你应该先看看你的朋友再走！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "你要我看谁？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你并不是第一个到这里送礼的人，还有人的想法也跟你一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "还有谁来送礼？送的是什么？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是一把剑。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "常无意？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "他的人也在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他来得比你早，我先见你，只因为你不说谎。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "坐。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你也来了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我也来了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你还好？",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "还好！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你杀人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "不但杀人，而且剥皮！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你能杀什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 350,
